This topic describes how to backup and restore the Pivotal Container Service control. PKS uses the [BOSH Backup and Restore](https://docs.cloudfoundry.org/bbr/index.html) framework for backing up and restoring the PKS deployment.

The control plane includes:
* The UAA mysql database
* The PKS API mysql database

No cluster data or deployed applications are backed up.

